    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 2 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_136011460297179197.png",
                "id": "talent70656",
                "key": "Strike of Fortune",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Strike of Fortune"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 3 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/7fae27e2ff070ba5aedf9d5c45e28d2e_6725740323677712874.png",
                "id": "talent92337",
                "key": "Passion Overload",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Passion Overload"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span>dan menciptakan<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Inspiration Field</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Inspiration Field</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karaktermu menggunakan Skill</span>: Jika Karakter ini memiliki minimal 7 poin HP, maka mengakibatkan +2 poin DMG tambahan untuk kasus ini; Setelah DMG Skill-nya selesai, jika HP Karakter ini tidak lebih dari 6 poin, maka memulihkan 2 poin HP untuk Karakter ini</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/bf3ffcaa5b9f41654043224fc74f3363_8634902504616193333.png",
                "id": "talent22411",
                "key": "Fantastic Voyage",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fantastic Voyage"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/10/1023623/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_1061926762930276489.png",
                "id": "talent19403",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3932415085855762793.png",
